yingyinNormal.en: No, it's another one, different owner, different part of town.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不，是另一个。不同的主人，不同的地点。

yingyinNormal.en: Plant cells make energy a different way.
yingyinNormal.zh: 植物细胞通过不同的形式制造能量。

yingyinNormal.en: Humanity has always feared that which is different.
yingyinNormal.zh: 人类总是畏惧和他们不同的东西。

yingyinNormal.en: Right. Different rules for us. Nice guy, artificial. Thank you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧， 评判我们的规则是不同的，人不错。但是个人工智能 。谢谢捧场。

yingyinNormal.en: Exactly, Harry. Exactly. Which makes you different from Voldemort.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这就对了，哈利，这就对了。这就是你跟伏地魔不同的地方。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets》

yingyinNormal.en: What's all this stuff? They're brochures from different adoption agencies.
yingyinNormal.zh: 嘿，这些是什么？哦，这些是我们从不同的领养中心找来的小册子。

yingyinNormal.en: From a different country, a different religion, a different look. And our first reaction to the unknown has always been fear.
yingyinNormal.zh: 来自其它国家，有着不同的信仰，长着不一样的面孔。我们对于未知者的第一反应总是害怕。

yingyinNormal.en: We'll put their names in bold, with different fonts, and I can use different colors for each column.
yingyinNormal.zh: 她俩的名字用不同字型的粗体字，然后每一栏可以用不同的颜色来写上。

yingyinNormal.en: Tall, beautiful, scary, a different sex, a different species, live-action, cartoon. It's all your call.
yingyinNormal.zh: 高大，漂亮，吓人，不同的性别，不同的物种，电影角色，甚至卡通人物。都你说了算。

yingyinNormal.en: Because different people are strong and weak at different things, most people can't do all five steps well.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不同的人在不同的事情上各有长短，大多数人不能良好地完成这五步。

yingyinNormal.en: So in some sense, when we have buyers and sellers and we have two different people from two different perspectives.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以某个程度上而言，买家和卖家是看事情角度完全不同的两个人群。

yingyinNormal.en: Centuries of living in different conditions, eating different food and encountering different neighbors turned similar dialects with varied pronunciation and vocabulary into radically different languages, continuing to divide as populations grew and spread out further.
yingyinNormal.zh: 几个世纪的不同生活条件，不同食物，不同邻居，使原本相似而只是发音和词汇有所不同的方言变成了完全不同的语言，并随着人口的增长和迁移不断分化。

yingyinNormal.en: Hundreds of different flowers, dozens of different colors, whether it be orange gazanias, purple dew flowers, or the red balloon pea plant.
yingyinNormal.zh: 百余种不同的花，十余种不同的颜色，从黄澄澄的勋章菊，到紫艳艳的露水花，再到红彤彤的球状豌豆花。

yingyinNormal.en: Every day, I walk through different neighborhoods, different communities, and becoming a part of them is as easy as stopping by to say hello.
yingyinNormal.zh: 每天，我都要经过不同的街坊，不同的社区，并且成为他们的一员，就像停下来问好一样简单。

yingyinNormal.en: No-no-no, I know, but you and I are different people though, and this is a totally different situation, and I know that I am not gonna regret this.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你不用说，我知道，不过你我是完全不同的人，而且情况也完全不同，我知道我这样做绝不会后悔。

yingyinNormal.en: How did you get two different kinds of dinosaurs to, you know...
yingyinNormal.zh: 你们怎么让两种不同的恐龙内啥，你懂的…

yingyinNormal.en: Four different women. I've had sex way more times. How many? Nine.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是四个不同的女人，次数就多太多了。几次？九次。

yingyinNormal.en: If you live long enough, you see the same eyes in different people.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果你活得够久，就能通过眼睛能看透不同的人。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah. Back then, cars came across the country a whole different way.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是的，以前车在州之间穿行的方法和现在是完全不同的

yingyinNormal.en: Go to a lot of different places and tell you if it's worth a weekend.
yingyinNormal.zh: 得去很多不同的地方，然后告诉大家值不值得去度周末。
